---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { url } from '../../utils';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Application Examples"
  description="Real-world examples of hospital acupuncture and acupressure implementation using the HAIF framework, including PONV acupressure at Northern Hospital and PANDA (acupuncture in the ED for acute pain)."
  lastReviewed="April 2026"
>
  <h1>Application Examples</h1>

  <p>
    These case studies show how the HAIF framework has been applied in real
    hospital settings. Each example walks through the four phases — Exploration,
    Preparation, Implementation, and Sustainment — as applied to a specific
    clinical context.
  </p>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Example 1: Acupressure for PONV</h3>
      <p>
        Nurse-led acupressure wristband implementation for post-operative
        nausea and vomiting at Northern Hospital, Victoria. A completed
        case study demonstrating all four phases.
      </p>
      <a href={url('/examples/ponv-acupressure/')}>View case study &rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>
        Example 2: PANDA — Acupuncture in the ED
        <span class="coming-soon">Coming Soon</span>
      </h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Personalised Acupuncture in the Northern Hospital Emergency
        Department for Acute Pain.</strong> Acupuncturist-delivered acupuncture
        for acute pain presentations. Research is currently in progress.
      </p>
      <em>Information to follow.</em>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom-line">
    <strong>Have an Implementation Story?</strong>
    If you have implemented acupuncture or acupressure in a hospital setting
    and would like your experience featured as a case study,
    <a href={url('/contact/')}>contact us</a>.
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
